{"prompt": "Design a responsive platform for a community sports club. The aesthetic should incorporate a dynamic emerald green.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Community Sports Club</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #2ecc71; /* Emerald Green */\n            --secondary-color: #a3e1c4; /* Lighter shade of green */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #f4f7f6;\n            --header-footer-bg: #27ae60; /* Darker green */\n            --card-bg: #ffffff;\n            --card-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: #333;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--header-footer-bg);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .content {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n        }\n\n        .section {\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .section h3 {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            display: inline-block;\n            padding-bottom: 5px;\n        }\n\n        .cards {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .card {\n            background-color: var(--card-bg);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);\n            padding: 30px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .card h4 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n        }\n\n        .card p {\n            color: #555;\n        }\n\n        .card a {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .card a:hover {\n            background-color: var(--header-footer-bg);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--header-footer-bg);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n            .hero h2 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1.1em;\n            }\n            nav a {\n                margin: 0 10px;\n                font-size: 0.9em;\n            }\n            .cards {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n            }\n            .container {\n                padding: 15px;\n            }\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 480px) {\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 1.8em;\n            }\n            .hero h2 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1em;\n            }\n            nav {\n                padding: 8px 0;\n            }\n            nav a {\n                display: block;\n                margin: 5px 0;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Community Sports Hub</h1>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n            <a href=\"#sports\">Sports</a>\n            <a href=\"#events\">Events</a>\n            <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Play. Connect. Grow.</h2>\n            <p>Your local hub for all things sports. Join our vibrant community and get active!</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"content\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"section\">\n                <h3>About Us</h3>\n                <p>We are a passionate community dedicated to promoting sports and healthy living. With a wide range of activities for all ages and skill levels, there's something for everyone.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"sports\" class=\"content\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"section\">\n                <h3>Our Sports</h3>\n                <div class=\"cards\">\n                    <div class=\"card\">\n                        <h4>Football</h4>\n                        <p>Join our weekly matches and training sessions. All levels welcome!</p>\n                        <a href=\"#\">Learn More</a>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"card\">\n                        <h4>Basketball</h4>\n                        <p>From casual pick-up games to competitive leagues, hit the court with us.</p>\n                        <a href=\"#\">Learn More</a>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"card\">\n                        <h4>Tennis</h4>\n                        <p>Sharpen your skills with our coaching programs and friendly tournaments.</p>\n                        <a href=\"#\">Learn More</a>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"card\">\n                        <h4>Running Club</h4>\n                        <p>Lace up and join our group runs for fitness and camaraderie.</p>\n                        <a href=\"#\">Learn More</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"events\" class=\"content\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"section\">\n                <h3>Upcoming Events</h3>\n                <div class=\"cards\">\n                    <div class=\"card\">\n                        <h4>Summer Tournament</h4>\n                        <p>Date: July 20th, 2024</p>\n                        <p>Details: Annual football and basketball tournament.</p>\n                        <a href=\"#\">Register</a>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"card\">\n                        <h4>Family Fun Day</h4>\n                        <p>Date: August 10th, 2024</p>\n                        <p>Details: Games and activities for the whole family.</p>\n                        <a href=\"#\">Details</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"content\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"section\">\n                <h3>Get In Touch</h3>\n                <p>Have questions or want to get involved? Reach out to us!</p>\n                <p>Email: info@communitysports.com</p>\n                <p>Phone: (123) 456-7890</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2024 Community Sports Hub. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>"}